==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: mail-order
<hw>mail-order</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<def>The buying and selling of goods to be shipped from the vendor
through the mail to the purchaser. Information about to be purchased may
be found in catalogs, advertisements, on the web, etc., and purchase
orders transmitted to the vendor by mail, telephone, or internet
connection.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>mail pouch</ent>⟦br⟧
